info.description:
Flywheel SDK
============

An SDK for interaction with a remote Flywheel instance.

Getting Started
===============

.. code-block:: python

    import flywheel
    from pprint import pprint

    fw = flywheel.Client('api-key')

    user = fw.get_current_user()
    pprint(user)

    fw.upload_file_to_project('project-id', '/path/to/file.txt')
